text: Eunidia stramentosipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1954.BioLib.cz - Eunidia stramentosipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1954
